r used to have the keys to lock of empty houses for sixpence a week to let the people look round the houses and some would - go into a clean house rather than having the one they were living in cleaned. Yes, in those days that was how it was. Yes. To get 
a clean house. And - but my father always used to say we got rid of a lot of rubbish when we changed houses.
