Well the two boys were in the top attic and - there was a bed put up in the bathroom for the elder sister, it was a very big long bathroom and - she thinks that's where she got her rheumatism from. Of course mother and father had the front bedroom, yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8851753 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16741939\charrsid3622924 
