Yes. My oldest sister played the piano beautifully, and George played the piano, you see that
 was my own mother's tuition, and - they used to bring various friends in on Sunday evenings and they used to have proper sing-songs. Yes. Either hymns or - popular songs or anything of that kind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8851753 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16741939\charrsid3622924 Where did your mother cook?
