Oh - an aunt came - two aunts came, one from Pontefract, one was a lady's maid in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}London{\*\xmlclose}, and her brother from {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Aldershot{\*\xmlclose}
. And of course all the family. I think that's - I think that was -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8851753 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16741939\charrsid3622924 What about mourning in those days?
