Oh yes. Yes. New - new black dresses or dressed dyed quickly and - new hats. Oh yes, it was deep mourning in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8851753 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16741939\charrsid3622924 How long did you stay in these mourning clothes?
