{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Aspley{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Park{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. Yes. And then we used to sing songs on the way back along {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}
