{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}St Ansell Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 I was always up in the top six. And - I was often called out to the front to - ask us - to ask the whole class a sum - that had been taught at the other school and I remember particula
rly once I'd asked a - a sum and I hadn't reckoned the answer myself. And how silly I felt when the teacher asked me what the answer was.
