Oh - in the summer we would walk round the Robin Hood's Chase and up Wells Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8851753 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16741939\charrsid3622924 Who would you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1922691 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16741939\charrsid3622924 A friend I'd met probably at work or - school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8851753 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16741939\charrsid3622924 Did you make any new friends, girls or boys, at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1922691 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16741939\charrsid3622924 G
irls I worked with. We would make up a three or foursome and - go - on the Forst or the Arbreton - that - the Arbreton was a very nice place to - to walk round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8851753 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16741939\charrsid3622924 Did you ever bring these friends home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1922691 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16741939\charrsid3622924 Oh no. No. Now Jessie made three friends at S
t Annes school and these three friends used to take it in turns to go to each others house for tea on Sunday. And of course Jessie was invited as a foursome. But when she asked could she bring them home - not likely. No. So of course that lost Jessie - sh
e dropped her friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8851753 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16741939\charrsid3622924 What do you think would have happened if your own mother had been alive?

